quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  57,1,"Whatever is in the heavens and earth exalts Allāh,{1} and He is the Exalted in Might, the Wise.",footnotes:1:1
  57,2,"His is the dominion of the heavens and earth. He gives life and causes death, and He is over all things competent."
  57,3,"He is the First{1} and the Last,{2} the Ascendant{3} and the Intimate,{4} and He is, of all things, Knowing.",footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2,footnotes:3:3,footnotes:4:4